## Introduction


The purpose of this audit is to ensure our technical infrastructure aligns with Forgotten Formula PMA's mission of prioritizing healing over profits, supporting nature-first methodologies, and fostering member sovereignty. This document presents a detailed analysis of simulated API error rates, system throughput, and proposes backend optimizations and database refactoring. We aim to contribute to our mission by enhancing the efficiency and reliability of our systems.


